  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Craft and Prepare:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Turn scavenged resources into valuable equipment. Assemble gear sets to arm your defenders for the battles ahead.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500910/extras/a7929b3330fd3c27ad07a704d8afe910.avif?t=1747411126\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Deep Progression System:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock over 400 progression nodes to gain powerful weapons, new buildings, and player upgrades. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500910/extras/a6547745565a426cce0ff4acc04f3583.avif?t=1747411126\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Scavenge the Battlefield:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore ancient battlefields to gather resources, tools, weapons, and armor. Pack your backpack strategically using a Tetris-style minigame.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500910/extras/5ab675595f74f3d7a94a85550debf6cb.avif?t=1747411126\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Rebuild and Expand the Bastion:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Construct and upgrade buildings, from warehouses and workshops to towering fortifications and training grounds. Build vertically on the massive Bastion wall for maximum efficiency.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500910/extras/3d909d0c400083096d7e0a311c00e4e8.avif?t=1747411126\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Defend Against the Undead:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prepare for relentless undead sieges by strategically positioning your defenders and optimizing your Bastion for survival in tactical siege simulations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500910/extras/b27ec5593e2234799bcd8bb8fedd6973.avif?t=1747411126\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p>",
