 by strategically positioning your defenders and optimizing your Bastion for survival in tactical siege simulations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3500910/extras/b27ec5593e2234799bcd8bb8fedd6973.avif?t=1747411126\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p>",
